snippet.title: JoJo Johnson x Austin - Trouble (Music Video)
snippet.description:
Hi guys!  Hope you enjoy JoJo Johnson x Austin's  new "Trouble" music video!

Let us know what YOU think about the music video in the comments below!

Like this channel and want to see more videos from MattyB, the Haschak Sisters & and all of their friends?  It's easy!  Simply LIKE, FAVORITE, COMMENT and SHARE this video with YOUR friends on YouTube!  ;)  You can also help spread the word with #funniflix and following us on social media! Feels so good

Chorus
(Not) getting in trouble 
Stay away
It’s going down, yes I came to play 
No trouble
Come my way
It’s no fun when I misbehave 
Not gonna let you get in trouble
Sorry if I burst your bubble
Hey, hey, hey
Ya it feels so good
(Not) getting in trouble 

Verse 1
He thinks he’s 
So smooth
On the move 
I’m 1 step ahead
I got him fooled 
You know we’re one in the same
Who am I kidding, I’m queen of the pranks! 
One, two 
Gonna stop you
Your tricks old news
But watch what I do
You’re gonna lose at your own game
That’s right, JoJo’s queen of the pranks!
